.Typescrpt allows js to write in much more precise way to get less errors.
.It gives type safety.
.it does static checking.
.it is a development tool our code still runs in js.
.to install- npm install -g typescript.
.declaring a variable:  let var_name: type=value;
.export{} -removes errors in ts if code is running fine in js.
. it also gives suggestion of variables and functions.

